f0ebeb09-4e1c-44b8-8972-2ffccf8b168b.title: Father Urhney
f0ebeb09-4e1c-44b8-8972-2ffccf8b168b.text:
I suppose I'd better talk to you then. What problems
has he got himself into this time?

options.text: He's got a ghost haunting his graveyard.
You mean he gets himself into lots of problems?

d252bced-9dbd-4a49-9f18-6cc5b7dba2a7.title: <player>
d252bced-9dbd-4a49-9f18-6cc5b7dba2a7.text: You mean he gets himself into lots of problems?

74096a63-518b-4638-af99-a8506101c1fb.title: Father Urhney
74096a63-518b-4638-af99-a8506101c1fb.text:
Yeah. For example, when we were trainee priests he
kept on getting stuck up bell ropes.

ac0939b5-b5e5-4e96-b99b-13c9856f2d1e.title: Father Urhney
ac0939b5-b5e5-4e96-b99b-13c9856f2d1e.text:
Anyway. I don't have time for chitchat. What's his
problem THIS time?

415288e5-76c7-4ede-9a63-9888dddd5f11.title: <player>
415288e5-76c7-4ede-9a63-9888dddd5f11.text: He's got a ghost haunting his graveyard.

ac113748-22d0-41c1-abf9-c7937e9a1ee6.title: Father Urhney
ac113748-22d0-41c1-abf9-c7937e9a1ee6.text:
I leave town for just five months, and ALREADY he
can't manage.

51c9ca87-7bc0-4aef-9165-e1c68866cf47.title: Father Urhney
51c9ca87-7bc0-4aef-9165-e1c68866cf47.text:
Well, I can't go back and exorcise it. I vowed not to
leave this place. Until I had done a full two years of
prayer and meditation.

eb2c2315-1c00-496d-a2b3-6f89b97f0830.title: Father Urhney
eb2c2315-1c00-496d-a2b3-6f89b97f0830.text: Tell you what I can do though; take this amulet.

8e358eb3-0fab-482e-86d8-47850983efc9.text: Father Urhney hands you an amulet.

121a64c7-9099-4d98-94ec-59abd8c17d49.title: Father Urhney
121a64c7-9099-4d98-94ec-59abd8c17d49.text: It is an Amulet of Ghostspeak.

6a4a9e42-c711-4824-a34e-a93554f560da.title: Father Urhney
6a4a9e42-c711-4824-a34e-a93554f560da.text:
So called, because when you wear it you can speak to
ghosts. A lot of ghosts are doomed to be ghosts because
they have left some important task uncompleted.

6d5a0bd1-b8b1-49c6-8a50-a8c0f6b53b8f.title: Father Urhney
6d5a0bd1-b8b1-49c6-8a50-a8c0f6b53b8f.text:
Maybe if you know what this task is, you can get rid of
the ghost. I'm not making any guarantees mind you,
but it is the best I can do right now.

920364fb-4616-4324-9a29-b29f00774f76.title: <player>
920364fb-4616-4324-9a29-b29f00774f76.text: Thank you. I'll give it a try!
